data.description:
Near brand new stunning Crestwood floor plan home in the luxury subdivision of Rivers Pointe Estates! Beautiful foyer opens to a flex space, private dining room, and butlers pantry that leads to the gourmet kitchen. The kitchen features an impressive island, granite countertops, double oven, and stainless steel Energy Star qualified appliances! Grand family room boasts stone fireplace and leads to the enclosed deck. The deck offers a private outdoor fireplace and stairs to the backyard. Off the kitchen, an incredible living space overlooking the wooded backyard, perfect for entertaining! The primary suite on the main level offers high tray ceilings, walk-in closet, and ensuite bath with soaking tub, shower, and double vanity. Upstairs, the loft can be customized to your needs and the 3 bedrooms are bright and spacious. The fully finished basement includes fifth bedroom, wet bar and walkout access to the patio and large private backyard. This estate with smart thermostat, 3 car garage, and luxury interior features is ready to move-in! 

Seller is willing to contribute $10,000 for an interest rate buy down. Please request more information if interested in utilizing this offering.
